{"tid":1713811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中大兒女，護我山城！","createTime":"2019-11-12T20:22:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T21:38:47.000Z","uid":280136,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b34c9c977c4355763a2a238e989ae63fcfd4b5c9","tid":1713811,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T20:22:24.000Z","msg":"首先好多謝各位中大人有E股勇氣同信念去守護我地嘅家園，原來CU人係唔止玩唔止dem beat，而係可以承繼創校先賢之火，E兩日完全見到果種絕不向共產暴政低頭嘅風骨，果種保家衛國嘅意志，真係令我三生有幸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n與此同時，好感謝各位手足係中大面臨圍攻嘅時候勇於出手開花援助我地，D綠曱甴出曬兵力攻我地嘅同時，其他區根本中空曬，地區嘅手足真係完全屌打綠色暴徒咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有無數嘅司機源源不斷咁送物資入黎，真係令我地好感動，真係睇到有出路有曙光，咁優秀嘅民族點可以輸啊大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今晚嘅中大，很冷，聞到有如烏克蘭刺骨嘅寒冬。冷風之中，卻送來一絲溫暖，就是那熾熱的革命之火<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中大兒女，護我山城<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港，時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54e4f8bf2503e572fe3a02dd72d9cd5d269127f3","tid":1713811,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T20:24:38.000Z","msg":"如果跟到呢幾步做 就好大機會贏返少少<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1713666\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1713666</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f00c1c120b8ee20d76bf04f2f6c8342418f8677f","tid":1713811,"uid":129990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T20:25:55.000Z","msg":"屌咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依家中大仲打緊仗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解個個覺得自己好似贏撚左咁"},{"pid":"d835710ce3ce5e0db32f8e3199c7995ca2b094ad","tid":1713811,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f00c1c120b8ee20d76bf04f2f6c8342418f8677f","tid":1713811,"uid":129990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T20:25:55.000Z","msg":"屌咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依家中大仲打緊仗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解個個覺得自己好似贏撚左咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T20:33:33.000Z","msg":"我明啊，未到天光都危險<br />\n但士氣E家嘢，比D正能量可以谷得好勁wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b93c6fb5b1220ce4032f24550c08328224e2b5fb","tid":1713811,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T21:38:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\n<br />\n最新<br />\n<br />\n‼️眾議院多數黨領袖關注大學受襲<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/LeaderHoyer/status/1194322000870854656?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLeaderHoyer%2Fstatus%2F1194322000870854656%3Fs%3D19&d=QaIhKqS2ROfvs0VeIWBCOns01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=34c30474\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLeaderHoyer%2Fstatus%2F1194322000870854656%3Fs%3D19&h=85f330df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/LeaderHoyer/status/1194322000870854656?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n‼️Sen. Cory Gardner (Colorado)<br />\n關注中大 支持香港<br />\n‼️‼️佢未cosponsor條Act 請佢幫忙‼️‼️<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenCoryGardner/status/1194341990655246346?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenCoryGardner%2Fstatus%2F1194341990655246346%3Fs%3D19&d=QaIhKqS2ROfvs0VeIWBCOns01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=812e8258\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenCoryGardner%2Fstatus%2F1194341990655246346%